MLee 2018/02/27

Updated and reran python code found from below sites.
Added comments about the changes in the code.

In order to run:
  1. download review ZIP file from <http://myleott.com/op-spam.html>
  2. download "GoogleNews-vectors-negative300.bin.gz" file from
    <https://code.google.com/archive/p/word2vec/#Pre-trained_word_and_phrase_vectors> 
    <https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B7XkCwpI5KDYNlNUTTlSS21pQmM/edit>
  3. place directories and files as shown on the 'folderScreenshot.jpg'
  
https://migsena.com/deceptive_spam_part_1/
https://migsena.com/deceptive-spam-review-detection-with-cnn-using-tensorflow-part-2/
